channel.title: Time to expand World 2
channel.description:
I plan on increasing the total accessible area in W2 by slightly over 50%, but I feel it might be unfair to do it at some random time. I think it would be more fair if everyone agreed on a time, so if they wish, they could be there to explore and build in the first few minutes of opening it up. So I'd like for you guys to post times when you could be on if you want to be there when it first opens.
I think probably the weekend would be best for everyone.

item.title: Time to expand World 2
item.dc:creator: @Tom Tom
item.description:
@Tom wrote:

Well the idea of W2 was to be limited, I think it’s enough for people to build new stuff. If we expand too big then it’ll be just like W1 with people being scattered around, we want people to make good use of space and resources in W2.

While I was expecting it to be a little bigger myself, it’ll do
